# ==============================================================================
# GITIGNORE FOR HIGH-FIDELITY BIONIC ARM sEMG DATASET
# ==============================================================================

# 1. Ignore everything by default
*

# 2. Allow Git to look inside directory structures (CRITICAL for subfolders)
!*/

# 3. Whitelist all Jupyter Notebook files anywhere in the directory tree
!*.ipynb

# 4. Whitelist Project Documentation and Assets
!README.md
!*.jpg
!*.png
!survey_responses.xlsx

# 5. Track the .gitignore file itself
!.gitignore